name: SuperPepeYoesh Has A New Mission
description: SuperPepeYoesh (S.P.Y) is determined to take $BRR to the moon and meet with the legendary TezTools ApeChad. Here you can see S.P.Y gazing back at the earth, as ApeChad is currently landing at TZ Moon Base on the horizon. Will S.P.Y be able to navigate through the dangerous diamond fields created by ApeChads rocket fuel?
